precis:
Amendments to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS which update the rules in Part XII
pertaining to special income tax deductions for taxpayers involved in the
production and processing of minerals, oil and gas, so that the rules will
correspond to recent amendments to the Income Tax Act (S.C. 1991, c. 49).
